Here's a line-by-line explanation of what the code does:

1. Import the required packages (i.e., "fmt", "io/ioutil", "net/http", and "strings").
2. Create the main function.
3. Perform an HTTP GET request to the provided URL and handle any errors.
4. Close the response body after the function ends.
